====== Release Notes 5.10 ======

GridWay 5.10 is the new stable version of the fifth series of the metascheduler.

Release date: 31st March, 2012

===== Improved BES and CREAM drivers =====

===== FHS-compliant installation =====

===== Changes in the scheduler to enqueue jobs =====

===== Other features ======

Retry job cancel operations
Show disk size and free space in GB when needed
Submit MPI jobs to GRAM4 with wrapper

===== Bug fixing =====

The following bugs have been fixed:
  * Bug #114 (http://dev.gridway.org/issues/114): GW does not retry after a recover failure
